item.title: Help - 508 compiling errors -
item.dc:creator: @justinxg27 justinxg27
item.description:
@justinxg27 wrote:

Use this batch file:

@echo off
cd ../src
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.player
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/player/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.player.update
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/player/update/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.player.items
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/player/items/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.player.misc
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/player/misc/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.player.combat
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/player/combat/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.io
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/io/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.io.packets
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/io/packets/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.net
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/net/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.util
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/util/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.world.mapdata
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/world/mapdata/*.java
echo Compiling palidino76.rs2.world.items
"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_21\bin\javac.exe" -cp . -d ../bin/ ./palidino76/rs2/world/items/*.java
pause

Of course remember to change it to your JDK version.
